    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_5187377321525544933.png",
                "key": "Whirling Scythe",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Whirling Scythe"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.<br>If an opposing character has <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen </span>or <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Mist Bubble Prison</span> attached, this character gains 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Energy</span>. (Once per Round)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Frozen</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p>Character cannot use Skills. (Lasts until the end of this Round)<br>When this character receives <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span> or<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> Physical DMG</span>, removes this effect and increases DMG taken by 2.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Mist Bubble Prison</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Character cannot use Skills.</span> (Lasts until the end of this Round)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/2139cdf27302ec3978e3ef0ec9730400_8458777763577143788.png",
                "key": "Slash of Surging Tides",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Slash of Surging Tides"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 3<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\"> Hydro DMG</span>. Creates 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Mist Bubble Slime</span> in your Hand.<br>(Characters with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Mist Bubble Slime </span>equipped can use the Technique: <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Bubble Battle Tactics</span>)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/28dd7cbc401fba1847d124b593b37cc2_8301601971624392366.png",
                "key": "Bubblefloat Blitz",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Bubblefloat Blitz"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Equipment Card</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Technique: </span>Bubble Battle Tactics<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span><br>(A character can only equip 1 Technique at a time)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4719186905986850843.png",
                "key": "Mist Bubble Slime ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/47f0e77e4279d21ba6bb0062db34d677_7008373981727448377.png",
                "title": "Mist Bubble Slime "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Technique</span></p><p>(Prepare for 1 turn) Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Mist Bubble Prison</span> to opposing character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Mist Bubble Prison</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Character cannot use Skills.</span> (Lasts until the end of this Round)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3217057872646806042.png",
                "key": "Bubble Battle Tactics",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Bubble Battle Tactics"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_1006011242185126099.png",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Pyro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_5752833547492705666.png",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Energy</span></strong><br>Characters must consume Energy to use their Elemental Bursts.<br>When characters use an Elemental Skill or a Normal Attack, they will gain 1 Energy.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Technique</span></strong></p><p>When the active character is equipped with a Technique card, they can use the corresponding Technique.<br>Using a Technique counts as a Combat Action. If the character is unable to use Skills due to conditions like Frozen, Petrification, or Stun, they are also unable to use the Technique.<br>Using a Technique is not considered as using a Skill. Therefore, it cannot trigger effects such as \"After using a skill\" or \"After the character triggers an Elemental Reaction.\" Damage dealt by using a Technique is not considered Damage dealt by the character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3600735375906361623.png",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
